These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
House: craftsman, art-deco
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, roller
There are 2 different nationalities: british, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse
2 different games are played: canasta, bridge
1. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| House    | art-deco   | craftsman        |
| Transport   | bus    | roller |
| Nationality     | pakistani  | british       |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | horse         |
| Game   | bridge | canasta      |

