1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Cigar         | prince   | swisher |
| Flower   | daffodil  | azalea     |
| Transport   | bike  | taxi        |
| Pet           | goat     | pony       |
| City         | boston | colone     |

